    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered like a member of the family, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it shows\u2014she\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking just as sharp as the day she left the showroom. There might be a tiny, almost invisible mark here or there from a few lucky Sunday drives, but honestly, you\u2019d have to be looking with a magnifying glass to find them. She runs like a dream and is ready for a new home where she'll be just as loved. Swing by, let's grab a coffee, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
